            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                τύχηι ἀγαθῆι θεο<supplied reason="lost">ῖς Σεβα</supplied>στοῖς Κα<supplied reason="lost">ίσαρσιν</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Πούβλιος Πομπώνιος <supplied reason="lost">Πουβλίο</supplied>υ υἱὸς Αἰλιανὸς λ<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἐκ τῶν</supplied> ἰδίων τό τε σειταποδοχ<supplied reason="lost">εῖον κ</supplied>ατεσκεύασεν καὶ τ<supplied reason="lost">ὴν <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἀνέθη</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>κεν οὐδέτερον ἐχούσης <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῆς πόλεως πρότερον <supplied reason="lost">ἐν δὲ τῇ σει</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>τοδείᾳ παρασχὼν τοῦ πυροῦ τὸν μόδιον δηναρίο<supplied reason="lost">ις <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="5"/>τειμὴν ἐπὶ τῷ ἀμετάθετον εἶναι τὸ χρῆμα καθι<supplied reason="lost">ερωμένον</supplied> <lb n="6"/>Μ(άρκου) Λυκό<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">φρονος</supplied> τοῦ Ἡρακλέωνος υἱοῦ διάτα&amp;lt;ξ&amp;gt;ις ἀνθ’ ὧν<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> λ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Βαριανοῦ Σώσπιδος <supplied reason="lost">ὧ</supplied>ν ὑπογραφ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> Augustas proximas et pecuniae et frumenti nomine <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>tisi <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>uo solvere debuit et frumenti poenam constitutam decreto ordi<supplied reason="lost">nis</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
